---
import { site } from "@/data/site";
import { withBase } from "@/lib/path";
---

<section class="relative isolate overflow-hidden bg-slate-900" data-vision-hero>
  <div class="relative isolate min-h-[520px] overflow-hidden sm:min-h-[600px] lg:min-h-[650px]">
    <img
      class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover object-[55%_48%]"
      src={withBase("/images/home-hero-family.png")}
      alt="푸른 공원에서 건강한 일상을 보내는 가족 이미지"
      loading="eager"
      decoding="async"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/26"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(12,25,38,0.55),rgba(12,25,38,0.18)_42%,rgba(12,25,38,0.34))]"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-44 bg-[linear-gradient(0deg,rgba(0,0,0,0.38),rgba(0,0,0,0))]"></div>
    <div class="container-page relative flex min-h-[520px] items-center justify-center px-5 pb-16 pt-28 text-center text-white sm:min-h-[600px] lg:min-h-[650px] lg:pt-32">
      <div class="max-w-5xl [text-shadow:0_3px_18px_rgba(0,0,0,0.44)]">
        <p class="mb-5 text-xs font-black tracking-[0.42em] text-emerald-100 sm:text-sm">VISION OF BIOLAB</p>
        <h1 class="text-[64px] font-light leading-none tracking-[0.04em] sm:text-[92px] lg:text-[118px]">
          {site.englishName}
        </h1>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-8 max-w-4xl text-lg font-black leading-8 text-white sm:text-2xl sm:leading-10">
          건강기능식품과 이너케어 브랜드로 건강한 일상의 기준을 만듭니다.
        </p>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-3xl text-sm font-bold leading-7 text-white/88 sm:text-base">
          여성과 아이의 건강을 위한 원료, 제품, 유통 경험을 연구합니다.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
